<sect1 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md338">
<title>helios::engine::modules::ai::systems</title><para>AI behavior processing systems.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md339">
<title>Overview</title><para>Systems that process AI components and update entity behavior. Registered with the GameLoop and executed during the appropriate phase.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md340">
<title>Systems</title><para><table rows="2" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>System  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ChaseSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Steers entities towards their chase targets  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md341">
<title>ChaseSystem</title><para>Processes entities with <computeroutput>ChaseComponent</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>SteeringComponent</computeroutput>, and <computeroutput>TranslationStateComponent</computeroutput>.</para>
<sect2 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md342">
<title>Behavior</title><para>1. <bold>Target Resolution</bold>: Looks up target entity by handle 2. <bold>Timer Update</bold>: Advances cooldown timer by delta time 3. <bold>Cooldown Check</bold>: Only updates direction when timer exceeds cooldown 4. <bold>Direction Calculation</bold>: Computes normalized vector from entity to target 5. <bold>Steering Update</bold>: Sets steering intent to face calculated direction</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="dir_d085c729ee8a56dff1cc9d67ead9cf36_1autotoc_md343">
<title>Required Components</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
